	<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>High-Speed FTP Solution</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1037/1037316.png" type="image/png">
    <style>
    /* General Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    color: #333;
}

.container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
}

/* Header Section */
.header-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    background-color: #3498db;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
}

.main-heading {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.intro {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.cta-btn {
    background-color: white;
    color: #3498db;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

.cta-btn:hover {
    background-color: #2980b9;
    color: white;
}

/* Features Section */
.features-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.section-heading {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: #2c3e50;
}

.feature-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 15px;
    margin: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 250px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
}

.feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

h3 {
    color: #3498db;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Process Section */
.process-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.step {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 300px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
}

.step h4 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #3498db;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    margin-top: 50px;
}

/* Animations */
@keyframes fadeIn {
    0% {
        opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 1;
    }
}

@keyframes fadeInUp {
    0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}
    
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="header-section">
            <h1 class="main-heading animate-header">High-Speed File Transfer with FTP</h1>
            <p class="intro animate-intro">Experience fast, secure, and reliable file transfers with our FTP solution, optimized for efficiency and performance.</p>
            <a href="#features" class="cta-btn animate-btn">Learn More</a>
        </section>

        <section class="features-section" id="features">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Why Choose FTP for File Transfers?</h2>
            <div class="feature-card animate-card">
                <h3>High-Speed Transfers</h3>
                <p>Our FTP servers are optimized for speed, ensuring that large files are transferred quickly with minimal downtime.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card animate-card">
                <h3>Reliability</h3>
                <p>FTP supports resuming interrupted transfers, ensuring files are never lost or corrupted during the process.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card animate-card">
                <h3>Security</h3>
                <p>Our FTP solution uses FTPS to encrypt your data, safeguarding your sensitive information during transfers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card animate-card">
                <h3>Versatility</h3>
                <p>FTP is compatible with a variety of operating systems and file types, making it a flexible solution for any file transfer need.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="process-section">
            <h2 class="section-heading">How It Works</h2>
            <div class="step animate-step">
                <h4>1. Account Setup</h4>
                <p>Register an account and receive your FTP credentials to access our file transfer system.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step animate-step">
                <h4>2. Connect to FTP</h4>
                <p>Use any FTP client or our web interface to log in securely and start uploading or downloading files.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step animate-step">
                <h4>3. Upload or Download Files</h4>
                <p>Drag and drop your files into the FTP client and let our system handle the rest.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 X Transfer Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
	